e significativa","guid":"NosS0hT7vkZsjxfyT7qlMw","children":[{"id":"166","parent":"165","text":"- Basada en HRCT anormales, PFTs, y mortalidad prematura","guid":"AKVrGRd-6xVDCVlCKZDHqg","children":[]},{"id":"167","parent":"165","text":"- Reportada en 10% a 18% de pacientes con RA","guid":"YR5gaRcVRNw-W6hxAoUEYw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"168","parent":"86","text":"- Factores de Riesgo para RA-ILD","guid":"YGFxBFaWS0ULubaba4GgiA","children":[{"id":"169","parent":"168","text":"- Edad avanzada","guid":"K0xoQkJ7kUVMYkqMRdxdWA","children":[]},{"id":"170","parent":"168","text":"- Sexo masculino","guid":"E_cJsACQnStLXvDTVEt5Aw","children":[]},{"id":"171","parent":"168","text":"- Exposición al tabaco","guid":"CIkIHzbDi71y12OodRLUnw","children":[]},{"id":"172","parent":"168","text":"- Sinovitis activa","guid":"KRm4pyiqgb1Osy0GX6TLeQ","children":[]},{"id":"173","parent":"168","text":"- Seropositividad para factor reumatoide y/o anti-CCP","guid":"PaZAAztCRPkvX3CtPkurHA","children":[]},{"id":"174","parent":"168","text":"- Polimorfismos en MUC5B","guid":"UsEwDnJoye9n3HLGM9-Qdw","children":[]}]},{"id":"175","parent":"86","text":"- Diagnóstico\\Nde RA-ILD","guid":"VynIADC6tpJsSZGeIxWmcA","children":[{"id":"176","parent":"175","text":"- Evaluación","guid":"BJncuyHDauRt9ywXGJDmbA","children":[{"id":"177","parent":"176","text":"- PFTs (Pruebas de Función Pulmonar)","guid":"IlQIDzlWHOps3F9vKt0QLg","children":[]},{"id":"178","parent":"176","text":"- Imágenes (principalmente HRCT)","guid":"cBmop1-zwxcf7-TNGTNhTg","children":[]},{"id":"179","parent":"176","text":"- Lavado broncoalveolar","guid":"CF5E1G6jEdN42CzHRgSE2A","children":[]}]},{"id":"180","parent":"175","text":"- HRCT:\\NEstándar de Oro","guid":"KeVWzCg3nXQEUC_0fKaG2w","children":[{"id":"181","parent":"180","text":"- Caracteriza patrón y severidad de ILD","guid":"GqBnY2wsorswhhdSJB52Lw","children":[]},{"id":"182","parent":"180","text":"- Excluye diagnósticos alternativos: infección, toxicidad pulmonar por fármacos, malignidad","guid":"EmS98mbqrC0N_fX_DzMkbw","children":[]}]},{"id":"183","parent":"175","text":"- Patrones en HRCT","guid":"KQj3o2NfFlc3TfMuLaLUXg","children":[{"id":"184","parent":"183","text":"- UIP (más común): fibrosis, reticulación, bronquiectasia por tracción, Panal de abeja","guid":"BSKBOyVFH0VGM7rKJ3aJSg","children":[]},{"id":"185","parent":"183","text":"- NSIP: menos común, reticulación + características inflamatorias (opacidades en vidrio esmerilado)","guid":"Xps8LzMQGjpSU5l4TrTk1g","children":[]},{"id":"186","parent":"183","text":"- Otros: neumonía organizativa, etc.","guid":"EsPdUXJDfkVn6EYkGyIiJg","children":[]}]},{"id":"187","parent":"175","text":"- Biopsia de Pulmón","guid":"YOaQGGDAcuthJqb-Csvm5Q","children":[{"id":"188","parent":"187","text":"- Reservada para patrones atípicos en HRCT (p. ej., enfermedad asimétrica, nódulos/cavitación)","guid":"CPgQYGV21vIHcm3AI5h3ww","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"189","parent":"86","text":"- Cribado para RA-ILD","guid":"eI4HJj1pG9Jt3QweIfDk8w","children":[{"id":"190","parent":"189","text":"- Importancia: Detección temprana ➜ Inicio oportuno del tratamiento","guid":"UaN5rTf4hRJHtu3yZAg3oA","children":[{"id":"191","parent":"190","text":"- Retraso en diagnóstico asociado a ↑ mortalidad","guid":"T85ugjvCuAtlrQTNLmmqsQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"192","parent":"189","text":"- Limitaciones\\Nde Cribado","guid":"VWGGWjoOvqwZAgD7dES3mg","children":[{"id":"193","parent":"192","text":"- Pacientes asintomáticos pueden tener RA-ILD","guid":"D8Oingw9XQo8MOB8SNec5g","children":[]},{"id":"194","parent":"192","text":"- PFTs y radiografía de tórax con limitaciones para detectar RA-ILD","guid":"NsasRzG_3b0HDhhqBpUayQ","children":[]},{"id":"195","parent":"192","text":"- HRCT es el estándar de oro pero no es factible para todos los pacientes","guid":"bYKVyWy7HTc0_sV6XFVoDg","children":[]}]},{"id":"196","parent":"189","text":"- Rol del Reumatólogo","guid":"btLSRTgAnkV9Ho-HAZavlw","children":[{"id":"197","parent":"196","text":"- Cribado de síntomas de afec